{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"b48bf05e06","title":"对《中央宣传部关于公开放映和批判〈北国江南〉、〈早春2月〉的请示报告》的批示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"729e39b4ba","index":0,"year":1964,"month":8,"day":null,"articleId":"b48bf05e06"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","name":"毛泽东思想万岁（1961年-1968年）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives3/main/45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"9a2f444b75","type":"paragraph","text":"息的人玩的。那些吃了饭没有事博做的人才有功夫养花弄花。","index":0,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"b48bf05e06"},{"id":"fb5db061ce","type":"paragraph","text":"全国解放已经十几年了，养花不但没有减少，反而比过去发展了，现在要改变。我就不喜欢房里摆花，白天好象有点好处，晚上还有害处。我的房子里的花早就让他们撤了，以后又让他们把院子里的花也撤了。你们在院子里种了一些树，不是满好喝？还可以再种。你们的花窖要取消。大部分花要减掉，只需少数人管理庭园。今后庭院要多种树，多种果树，还可以种点粮食、蔬荣、油料作物。北京市区中的公园和香山要逐步改种这些果树和油料作物，这样既好看，又实惠，对子孙后代有好处。","index":1,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"b48bf05e06"},{"id":"f858704168","type":"paragraph","text":"观看北京京剧一团演出的革命现代京刷《沙家滨》的指示","index":2,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"b48bf05e06"},{"id":"e550b976b7","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六四年七月）","index":3,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"b48bf05e06"},{"id":"5d7c7f4382","type":"paragraph","text":"要突出武装斗争，强调武装的革命消灭武装的反革命，戏的结尾要正面打进去。加强军民关系的戏，加强正面人物的音乐形象。","index":4,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"b48bf05e06"},{"id":"0d7efd23a6","type":"paragraph","text":"关于部队学习游泳的批示","index":5,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"b48bf05e06"},{"id":"1efa146301","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六四年八月六日）","index":6,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"b48bf05e06"},{"id":"55f405be5e","type":"paragraph","text":"此件看了，很好。是否在一切有条件的地方，部队的大多数人都可以试验学游泳？军委是否已发出了指示？","index":7,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"b48bf05e06"},{"id":"c679a949d1","type":"paragraph","text":"条件不好，主要是：（一）有吸血虫及其他毒害的河流、池塘：（二）有大游涡的河流地段；（三）有效鱼的海中。此外，部队中总有一部分不适宜于游水的，不要强合人人都下水。","index":8,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"b48bf05e06"},{"id":"0673664cce","type":"paragraph","text":"对卫生部党粗关于高干部","index":9,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"b48bf05e06"},{"id":"5a8efc99d9","type":"paragraph","text":"保健工作报告的批示","index":10,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"b48bf05e06"},{"id":"192d6d8ab3","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六四年八月）“保健局应当取消。”“北京医院医生多，病人少，是一个老爷医院，应当开放。”","index":11,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"b48bf05e06"},{"id":"af05d6449a","type":"paragraph","text":"对《中央宣传部关于公开放映和批判","index":12,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"b48bf05e06"},{"id":"34a9be5b7f","type":"paragraph","text":"《北国江南》、早春二月）","index":13,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"b48bf05e06"},{"id":"5c47daa15c","type":"paragraph","text":"的请示报告》的批示","index":14,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"b48bf05e06"},{"id":"5eca805d01","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六四年八月）可能不只这两部影片，还有别的都需要批制。使修正主义材料公布于众。","index":15,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"b48bf05e06"},{"id":"9ed19f6055","type":"paragraph","text":"147","index":16,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"b48bf05e06"}],"page":{"id":"8f6feb760d","publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"b48bf05e06","start":160,"end":160}}}},"__N_SSG":true}